text: Jan Gundersrud (born 25 November 1966) is a Norwegian former shooter who competed with the rifle. He represented Norway at the 1988 Summer Olympics, where his best result was 9th place. == External links == * Category:Shooters at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Norwegian sport shooters Category:Shooters at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:1966 births == References == Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Olympic shooters of Norway
